4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" where individuals can start a career as a data scientist and build their first ML models. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. It is a 16-week program that covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms such as Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course includes real-life case studies, industry-standard tools, and the opportunity to develop A.I. projects from development to deployment and maintenance. The classes are taught in English or Spanish, and the syllabus and content can be chosen accordingly. The course is taught by experienced instructors, including Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. Upon completion, students will receive a recognized certificate.
For more information, visit: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop